These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, blueberry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, badminton
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is not the person eating blueberry##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | blueberry   | lettuce  |
| Sport   | biathlon | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cherry, apricot
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person eating apricot##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | cherry | apricot      |
| Pet    | chinchilla  | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
