.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-6::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, techno
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, australian
1. the fan r&b is on the far right##1
2. the fan techno is not the pakistani##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | r&b      |
