.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  scientist, firefighter
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, snake
1. the scientist is in an odd position##4
2. the scientist is not the owner of the snake##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | scientist | firefighter |
| Pet   | rabbit       | snake       |

